column5: WOOO HOOO!  My box of fishing goodies came last night!!!  I was nice and let my husband open it..but he didn't get to steal any lures yet!  THANKS Dave, am really looking forward to using them, once the ice is off the St. Lawrence  Tamara
Thank you Dave... the wait was WELL worth it.  Good luck this season on the water and with the show.              ...Terry... We'll talk buddy ! LOL
Wait... when do I get my package from Mr Mercer... tell me that theres one coming for me too...
I think he put all three winners stuff in my box. Sorry !
wow that's cool and just for watching his first show on WFN
*drool*
There ya go Wayne... Some nice looking stuff there, looks like ya got a new arsenal. Good on ya Dave
Wow, that's amazing Wayne     Right on Dave !!!!!!!!  And look at that, an excuse for another post count  Joey

~~~Now let me see  Need it, need it, got it got it got it, need it need it, can always use another Tee shirt need it got it got it never seen that one before, need it got it. oh that enough for now, share with the others

Don't worry oldphart.. any that know me know that it will get shared amongst some OFC'rs. I could never use up these plastics as it's not in my fishing style. Maybe it should be and I could stop posting landscape pictures... but I've always been a meat and potatos kinda guy and it's hard to switch tactics.
Very nice prize pack there wayne !!!...lots of goodies,that should keep you busy for a while !!...
Old dog new trick thing? Dont worry Wayne, we'll learn ya eventually.....  Nice haul BTW!
Congrats on the haul, some great baits there for sure.
Very nice...
Great stuff Wayne!!!
Wayne, thats crazy!!! should keep you tocked up for a while!! nice job Dave!
Lools like someone is going to have to start bidding on yet another tackle storage system!LOL Congrats Wayne! HH
Wow, congrats Wayne. Let me know if you need any help testing those things out
Congrats, Imperial Angler  Dave really does a nice gift package,,, let me know if you need my address

And the big man keeps on giving!    I'd have done the same photo spread as Wayne but my cat was getting a bit too interested so I took a quick shot and put them away til the summer.  Of course with this wonderful box of goodies showing up and Snags summer picture post I'm going into serious withdrawl now.  Anyone else up for a drive down south?  Big thanks to Dave Mercer and TJ for putting this together.   Keep up the great shows Dave, gotta do one with the 10" swimbaits in the box - those are gonna be a learning experience for me all right.  Sean
Sigh.  I don't have my box of goodies yet!!!  I can't wait to get it though, my husband is itching to get his hands on MY lures!  Will post it when it arrives, HOPEFULLY today.
Nice box of lures for sure!  Mike
nice score!
hey....thats sweet!!!!
nice haul!
